OL,3,CStarmer's time to go and for leader
OL,4,Cwith 'more charisma', says Welsh
OL,5,CLabour MP
OL,7,FA senior Welsh Labour MP has said Sir
OL,8,FKeir Starmer should not lead the party
OL,9,Finto the next general election.
OL,11,FRuth Jones, who chairs the Welsh
OL,12,FAffairs Committee, said that the Prime
OL,13,FMinister had "done a great job" but
OL,14,Fthat it was time for him to "set out
OL,15,Fhis own timetable" to step down.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/8
