OL,3,CStarmer's time to go and for leader
OL,4,Cwith 'more charisma', says Welsh
OL,5,CLabour MP
OL,7,FLabour suffered losses in elections
OL,8,Facross the UK on Thursday. In last
OL,9,Fweek's Senedd Election, Plaid Cymru
OL,10,Fwon the most seats - the first time in
OL,11,Fhistory a party other than Labour have
OL,12,Fhad the largest amount of Senedd seats.
OL,14,FSir Keir Starmer is now facing
OL,15,Fpressure from within his party to quit
OL,16,Fbut vowed to prove his doubters wrong
OL,17,Fat a press conference on Monday.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
