PN,46203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1778580402
OL,3,CStarmer's time to go and for leader
OL,4,Cwith 'more charisma', says Welsh
OL,5,CLabour MP
OL,7,F"He turned the party around, he got us
OL,8,Fin in 2024 with an over 100 majority
OL,9,Fwhich is something nobody else has
OL,10,Fdone, so we'll always be grateful for
OL,11,Fthat," Ms Jones told ITV News.
OL,13,F"He's been leader for six years now
OL,14,Fand now it's time for him to set out
OL,15,Fhis own timetable to say, 'I will step
OL,16,Fdown, this is the timetable,' and
OL,17,Fsomebody else will lead us into the
OL,18,Fnext general election."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUzD@WO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/8
