PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1778580402
OL,3,CStarmer's time to go and for leader
OL,4,Cwith 'more charisma', says Welsh
OL,5,CLabour MP
OL,7,FShe added: "Keir has done a great job
OL,8,Fand we thank him very much but now is
OL,9,Fthe time for someone else with a
OL,10,Fdifferent personality, more charisma,
OL,11,Fa more go-get-it attitude to say,
OL,12,F'This is what the Labour Party is'
OL,13,Fbecause at the moment, we're not
OL,14,Fgetting that message across."
OL,16,FLord Peter Hain, a former Secretary of
OL,17,FStates for Wales and MP for Neath,
OL,18,Fsaid Sir Keir Starmer "is fighting
OL,19,Fback" but that he and the Labour party
OL,20,Fneed to "change radically".
OL,26,@oD@LOUvD@]O]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/8
