PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1778580402
OL,3,CStarmer's time to go and for leader
OL,4,Cwith 'more charisma', says Welsh
OL,5,CLabour MP
OL,7,FSpeaking to ITV News, Lord Hain said:
OL,8,F"Today's events show that the Prime
OL,9,FMinister is fighting back. It'll only
OL,10,Fbe time as to whether he's done enough
OL,11,Fand can really listen to people and
OL,12,Fact accordingly rather than continue
OL,13,Falong the failed path of the past few
OL,14,Fyears."
OL,16,FIn response to being asked whether he
OL,17,Fthinks Sir Keir should stand down, he
OL,18,Fadded: "I don't think the country
OL,19,Fwants the psychodrama of a fifth Prime
OL,20,FMinister in four years.
OL,26,@vD@GO]zD@HOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/8
