CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1778580402
OL,3,CStarmer's time to go and for leader
OL,4,Cwith 'more charisma', says Welsh
OL,5,CLabour MP
OL,7,F"That's what they rejected under the
OL,8,FConservatives but Keir Starmer and the
OL,9,Fgovernment and the Welsh Labour Party
OL,10,Fhave to change. We have to listen to
OL,11,Fpeople and reflect on that and change
OL,12,Fradically."
OL,14,FLord Hain said Thursday's result was a
OL,15,F"bad result" for Labour but
OL,16,F"predictable."
OL,26,@wD@AOUwD@LO]xD@AOUxD@NO]
