OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1778580402
OL,3,CStarmer's time to go and for leader
OL,4,Cwith 'more charisma', says Welsh
OL,5,CLabour MP
OL,7,F"There was a particular clear
OL,8,Falternative in Plaid Cymru and some
OL,9,FLabour supporters voted Reform but
OL,10,Fmost went Green or Plaid Cymru," he
OL,11,Ftold ITV Cymru Wales.
OL,13,F"So, we have to learn from that and
OL,14,Funderstand why that happened and renew
OL,15,Fthe party and the leadership,
OL,16,Fparticularly in London, and the Prime
OL,17,FMinister needs to listen to the people
OL,18,Fmuch more."
